{"tid":1180312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[避開71]送中惡法 擬6.27表決","createTime":"2019-05-31T17:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T18:08:04.000Z","uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd25a6b57066fb4f107b6f673ce11af902b2bf01","tid":1180312,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157704487962448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157704487962448%2F&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=6bb2752a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157704487962448/</a><br />\n<br />\n【A1頭條】港府前日就《 逃犯移交 》修訂，提出「小修小補」的新修訂拉攏商界支持，圖盡快通過惡法，有建制派披露，政府擬本月27日表決方案，民主派指政府明顯想避開 7.1 大遊行。民主派昨請政府交代如何協助被「送中」後遭不公平審訊、人權被侵犯的問題，律政司司長鄭若驊竟稱，有關人士可在內地提出申訴，民主派為之咋舌，不滿鄭無視內地冤案受害人申訴無門之苦。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨2點半，日報內容新鮮出爐！登入蘋果日報網站/動新聞app有得睇！<br />\n==============<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道立法會<br />\n（資料來源：民陣）<br />\n==============<br />\n剖析真相 守護公義<br />\n按此免費訂閱支持蘋果 無阻盡覽<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/J5m3Wamt7V\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2FJ5m3Wamt7V&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=e49534f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/J5m3Wamt7V</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">八婆已經好心急想香港快d死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月9號唔出黎，香港就真係endgame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cc51086030b878f2f167f12ae936e6cd9bb34284","tid":1180312,"uid":60665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"記得簽埋白宮聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-